Jerome Vouillon wrote:
> 
> What about the following syntax?
> - The comment is before the element:
>       (** fun 1 *)
>       val f : t
>       (** fun 2 *)
>       val g : u
> - The comment is after the element:
>       val f : t
>         (* fun 1 **)
>       val g : u
>         (* fun 2 **)

I like this -- it's an elegant solution that lets both styles coexist
naturally.

Eric
